views.markdown: If you need help with "Joox Premium", you can contact pxcex, the developer, via e-mail.
pxcex is the maintainer of the package "Joox Premium". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "pxcex repo" repo, pxcex.
